1. *Smatram* da je dobra ideja. (I think it's a good idea.)
2. On je *smatrao* da je to pogrešno. (He thought it was wrong.)
3. *Smatraju* da će u budućnosti biti još bolje. (They believe it will be even better in the future.)
4. Njegova porodica *smatra* da je on odgovoran. (His family thinks he is responsible.)
5. Ona *smatra* da je u redu da ide. (She thinks it's okay to go.)
6. *Smatramo* da je to najbolji način da se postigne cilj. (We consider this to be the best way to achieve the goal.)